{"tid":642354,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"官方：張伯倫因膝傷賽季報銷，並無緣俄羅斯世界杯","createTime":"2018-04-25T17:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T02:37:12.000Z","uid":20634,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0afa1606c87f6c77e69d87938c21de6bffb2a4cb","tid":642354,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T17:16:29.000Z","msg":"4月25日訊 利物浦官方消息稱，由於週二對陣羅馬比賽中的膝蓋傷勢，張伯倫將會因此賽季報銷，同時還將錯過今年夏天的國家隊比賽。週三，張伯倫接受了俱樂部隊醫的詳細檢查，目前俱樂部還沒有詳細的回歸時間表。<br />\n<br />\n《每日鏡報》消息稱，利物浦方面希望張伯倫可以在下賽季初期痊癒歸隊。這名球員已經在周三接受了詳細的檢查，週二對陣羅馬的歐冠比賽中，張伯倫因為膝蓋受傷提前被換下，他在比賽中對科拉羅夫進行鏟搶時膝蓋受傷。高普賽后也曾表示：&ldquo;張伯倫，可能是遭遇了很嚴重的傷病。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.hoopchina.com.cn/uploads/star/event/images/180425/b8ce41e2e186953e2db722103a69a07df16f109a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.hoopchina.com.cn%2Fuploads%2Fstar%2Fevent%2Fimages%2F180425%2Fb8ce41e2e186953e2db722103a69a07df16f109a.jpg&h=d2890468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsor屎:<a href=\"http://www.liverpoolfc.com/news/first-team/299571-liverpool-fc-alex-oxlade-chamberlain-injury-update\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.liverpoolfc.com%2Fnews%2Ffirst-team%2F299571-liverpool-fc-alex-oxlade-chamberlain-injury-update&d=e%2BbPU5a5VNOom2vgjLfwyP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=1da43268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.liverpoolfc.com/news/first-team/299571-liverpool-fc-alex-oxlade-chamberlain-injury-update</a>"},{"pid":"f5a818568ada4be2769d5872706c16500b3dc37b","tid":642354,"uid":581,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T17:17:49.000Z","msg":"連續兩次世界盃因為傷冇得踢"},{"pid":"8da8a895f2e607da24e7d339294b3e2b708a079a","tid":642354,"uid":36497,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T17:22:20.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa0355a8df80b719c884c20d32d69c342c66350","tid":642354,"uid":22589,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTim